ens-foil-siren-player-aid-cards-promo","canonical_link":"https://boardgamegeek.com/cardset/99167/sirens-foil-siren-player-aid-cards-promo"}]},"linkcounts":{"boardgamedesigner":1,"boardgamesolodesigner":0,"boardgameartist":1,"boardgamepublisher":1,"boardgamedeveloper":1,"boardgamegraphicdesigner":1,"boardgamesculptor":0,"boardgameeditor":1,"boardgamewriter":0,"boardgameinsertdesigner":0,"boardgamehonor":0,"boardgamecategory":2,"boardgamemechanic":3,"boardgameexpansion":0,"boardgameversion":1,"expandsboardgame":0,"boardgameintegration":0,"contains":0,"containedin":0,"reimplementation":0,"reimplements":0,"boardgamefamily":4,"videogamebg":0,"boardgamesubdomain":0,"boardgameaccessory":0,"cardset":2},"secondarynamescount":0,"alternatenamescount":0,"primaryname":{"nameid":"2229482","name":"Sirens","sortindex":"1","primaryname":"1","translit":"Sirens"},"alternatenames":[],"description":"<p>At long last, a lost ship has sailed into your cove! Is your song strong enough to attract the sailors away from it? On the opposite side of the cliff, another siren is surely preparing to fill the evening with notes meant to allure our new guests, as well.<br />\nWill that song overpower yours, or can you gather more sailors to your side of the cliffs?</p>\n\n<p>Sirens is a quick and compact micro drafting game for 1 to 2 players, in which you&rsquo;ll draft cards over the course of 2 to 3 rounds to construct a song to lure sailors away from the nearby ship. The player who successfully attracts 2 of the 3 sailors with their music will win the game!</p>\n\n<p>The game lasts for 2 or 3 rounds. Each round consists of 2 identical phases in which players draft cards, and then build a &ldquo;song&rdquo; with the cards that they kept. Each player&rsquo;s &ldquo;song score&rdquo; will be totaled on 4 conditions, and the winning song then takes a facedown card as a sailor. The first player with 2 sailors wins!</p>\n\n<p><em>&mdash;description from the publisher</em></p>\n\n","wiki":"<span class='